---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Game Design Concepts â€” Max Burkhardt">
  <article class="page">
    <header class="header">
      <h1>Game Design Concepts</h1>
      <p>
        Concept pitches, drawings, and references I use to explore ideas and player experience.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="block">
      <h2>Slime Boss Mass &amp; Health Concept</h2>
      <p>
        The idea: a slime boss whose health is its mass. As it loses mass, it becomes faster,
        more aggressive, and changes its attack patterns.
      </p>

      <img
        src="/design/slime-boss-sketch.png"
        alt="Slime boss sketches"
        class="inline-image"
      />

      <p>
        Early sketches focus on clearly showing mass changes to the player so they can
        understand when the boss is entering a new phase.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <h2>Concept PowerPoint</h2>
      <p>
        My Concept pitch about my 3 concepts, Mass Of Slime, Tokyo Park, Meandering Siege.
      </p>

      
      <div class="ppt-wrapper">
        <iframe
          src="https://1drv.ms/p/c/bafbd1724da29ef0/IQQtCgJLioqeQIhiyBb7dLPjASH0OQdk1UwEOLN2QYIWY78"
          width="100%"
          height="480"
          frameborder="0"
          scrolling="no"
        ></iframe>
      </div>

    </section>

    <section class="block">
      <h2>More concepts</h2>
      <p>
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>

  <style>
    .page {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem 3.5rem;
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .header p {
      max-width: 40rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .block {
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .block h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .block p {
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .inline-image {
      max-width: 100%;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin: 0.5rem 0 0.8rem;
    }

    .ppt-wrapper {
      margin: 1rem 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .hint {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>